{"id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0003","text":"偏偏愛得天都覺得猜不到","structure":{"line_index":3,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","不可思議","猜測"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["愛","猜不到","天"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,3,4,3,3,3,4,3,3,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["pin1","pin1","oi3","dak1","tin1","dou1","gok3","dak1","caai1","bat1","dou3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"偏偏","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"愛得天","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"覺得","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"猜","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不到","pos":"PART"}],"syntax_notes":"「偏偏」表示出乎意料，「愛得天」是誇張用法，表達愛情的不可思議，連老天爺都猜不到。"},"source":{"title":"劍龍在草地散步","artists":["薛凱琪"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2008","prev_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0002","next_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0004","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0004","text":"或者更感動","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":5},"semantics":{"themes":["情感","感動"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["感動"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,9,9,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["waak6","ze2","gam2","dung6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"或者","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"更","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"感動","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"簡短的句子，表達一種更深層次的感動，語氣帶有推測但肯定。"},"source":{"title":"劍龍在草地散步","artists":["薛凱琪"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2008","prev_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0005","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0005","text":"陪着我到風雨下星月時感覺沒人類更好","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":17},"semantics":{"themes":["陪伴","自然","幸福"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["陪伴","風雨","星月","人類","更好"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,5,4,3,5,2,3,2,0,9,4,2,0,2,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["pui4","zoek6","ngo5","dou3","fung1","jyu5","haa6","sing1","jyut6","si4","gam2","gok3","mut6","jan4","leoi6","hou2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"陪","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"着","pos":"PART"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"到","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"風雨","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"下","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"星月","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"時","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"感覺","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"沒","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"人類","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"更好","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"長句，描繪在惡劣天氣下與愛人陪伴的場景，強調這種時刻比任何人類的幸福都好，情感強烈。"},"source":{"title":"劍龍在草地散步","artists":["薛凱琪"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2008","prev_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0006","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0006","text":"到天邊散步難道要贊同","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["自由","質疑","接受"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["天邊","散步","贊同"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,3,3,9,2,0,2,4,4,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["dou3","tin1","bin1","saan2","bou6","naan4","dou6","jiu3","zaan3","tung4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"到","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"天邊","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"散步","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"難道","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"贊同","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「難道」表示疑問，質疑到天邊散步是否需要得到贊同，帶有對自由的嚮往和對束縛的質疑。"},"source":{"title":"劍龍在草地散步","artists":["薛凱琪"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2008","prev_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0007","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0007","text":"那句說話意識不好 那句說話華麗不到","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":16},"semantics":{"themes":["溝通","評價","不足"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["說話","意識","不好","華麗","不到"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,4,4,2,4,3,3,9,5,4,4,2,0,2,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["naa5","geoi3","syut3","waa6","ji3","sik1","bat1","hou2","naa5","geoi3","syut3","waa6","waa4","lai6","bat1","dou3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"那句","pos":"DET"},{"text":"說話","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"意識","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"不好","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"那句","pos":"DET"},{"text":"說話","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"華麗","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"不到","pos":"PART"}],"syntax_notes":"重複結構，描述說話的內容，一個是「意識不好」，另一個是「華麗不到」，都表達了溝通上的不足或不滿。"},"source":{"title":"劍龍在草地散步","artists":["薛凱琪"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2008","prev_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0008","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0008","text":"與你那個世界奇妙卻古老","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["世界觀","奇妙","古老"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["世界","奇妙","古老"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,5,4,4,4,0,2,4,9,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jyu5","nei5","naa5","go3","sai3","gaai3","kei4","miu6","koek3","gu2","lou5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"與","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"那個","pos":"DET"},{"text":"世界","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"奇妙","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"卻","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"古老","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"描述與「你」相關的世界，同時具有「奇妙」和「古老」的特質，形成一種對比和獨特的氛圍。"},"source":{"title":"劍龍在草地散步","artists":["薛凱琪"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2008","prev_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0009","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0009","text":"彷彿你原是 劍龍 我看我就是青草","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["身份認同","比喻","自然"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["劍龍","青草","彷彿"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,3,5,0,2,4,0,5,4,5,2,2,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["fong2","fat1","nei5","jyun4","si6","gim3","lung4","ngo5","hon3","ngo5","zau6","si6","cing1","cou2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"彷彿","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"原是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"劍龍","pos":"PROPN"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"看","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"就是","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"青草","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"運用「劍龍」和「青草」的比喻，將「你」比作稀有的劍龍，「我」比作普通的青草，形成強烈對比，但語氣是接納的。"},"source":{"title":"劍龍在草地散步","artists":["薛凱琪"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2008","prev_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0010","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0010","text":"即使不登對 也好","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":7},"semantics":{"themes":["接受","關係"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["登對","也好"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,9,3,3,4,5,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zik1","si2","bat1","dang1","deoi3","jaa5","hou2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"即使","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"不登","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"對","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"也好","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"「即使」表示讓步，「也好」表達一種無所謂的接受，即使不登對也沒關係。"},"source":{"title":"劍龍在草地散步","artists":["薛凱琪"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2008","prev_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0009","next_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0011","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0011","text":"與你那套愛法人類怕知道","structure":{"line_index":11,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","秘密","恐懼"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["愛法","人類","怕","知道"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,5,4,4,4,0,2,4,3,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jyu5","nei5","naa5","tou3","oi3","faat3","jan4","leoi6","paa3","zi1","dou6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"與","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"那套","pos":"DET"},{"text":"愛法","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"人類","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"怕","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"知道","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"描述「你」獨特的愛的方式，人類害怕被知道，暗示這種愛可能不被世俗接受。"},"source":{"title":"劍龍在草地散步","artists":["薛凱琪"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2008","prev_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0010","next_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0012","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0012","text":"方使我們像最初 生於的始祖 都好","structure":{"line_index":12,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["起源","本質","接受"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["最初","始祖","都好"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,9,5,0,2,4,3,3,3,3,9,9,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["fong1","si2","ngo5","mun4","zoeng6","zeoi3","co1","sang1","jyu1","dik1","ci2","zou2","dou1","hou2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"方使","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我們","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"像","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"最初","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"生於","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"始祖","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"好","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"「方使」表示結果，「都好」表達一種積極的肯定，認為像最初的始祖一樣活著，是好的。"},"source":{"title":"劍龍在草地散步","artists":["薛凱琪"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2008","prev_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0011","next_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0013","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0013","text":"你用存在發現時代太笨重","structure":{"line_index":13,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["時代","存在","批判"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["存在","發現","時代","笨重"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,2,0,2,4,2,0,2,4,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["nei5","jung6","cyun4","zoi6","faat3","jin6","si4","doi6","taai3","ban6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"用","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"存在","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"發現","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"時代","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"太","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"笨重","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"「你」的存在被用來發現時代的「笨重」，帶有對時代的批判和不滿。"},"source":{"title":"劍龍在草地散步","artists":["薛凱琪"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_2008","prev_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0012","next_line_id":"lyr_6Jab5Yev55Cq_MjAwOA_0014","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
